   Thursday's Markets:
   Wary Mood
   Dampens
   U.S. Trading
   ---
   Fears About Tokyo,
   U.S. Economy Keep
   Stocks, Bonds Flat
   ----
   By Douglas R. Sease
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
